In horseracing, Camelot trained by Aidan O'Brien, wins the Epsom Derby with 2,000 Guineas Stakes classes double. Also, with his son Joseph, become the first father son to win The Derby. (BBC)In 2014 FIFA World Cup qualification – UEFA Group C, Republic of Ireland lose 6–1 to Germany, their joint worst ever competitive defeat and their worst home defeat since 1931. Calls increase for the removal of manager Giovanni Trapattoni. (ESPN) (The Irish Times) (Deutsche Welle) (The Times of India)